comments:
I have installed Callisto M5 without C/C++

copy mindmap.ecore into a GMF project. right-click mindmap.ecore, select initialize ecore_diagram. In the Wizard click on finish. The wizard doesn't vanish. no ecore_diagram is created.
See the attached log.

Remarks: 
1. you see the -clean argument at startup. The same happens without this argument.
2. I have the GMF taipan example in my workbench from HEAD. This version doesn't fit to callisto M5. This is in the log file but I think you can ignore this.

The antlr dependency is going to be removed shortly on the OCL component. The OCL component will be self contained and does not require any third party downloads.
